quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  80,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  80,1,( Mohammad mstfe? ) tursh roo hue aur munh phair baithy
  80,2,ke un ke paas aik nabina aaya
  80,3,aur tum kokiya khabar shayad woh pakizgee haasil karta
  80,4,ya sochta to samjhaana usay faida deta
  80,5,jo parwa nahi karta
  80,6,is ki taraf to tum tavajja karte ho
  80,7,halaank agar woh nah sanwre to tum par kuch ( ilzaam ) nahi
  80,8,aur jo tumahray paas dorta howa aaya
  80,9,aur ( khuda se ) darta hai
  80,10,is se tum be rukhi karte ho
  80,11,dekho yeh ( quran ) nasiyaat hai
  80,12,pas jo chahay usay yaad rakhay
  80,13,qabil adab warqon mein ( likha howa )
  80,14,jo buland maqam par rakhay hue ( aur ) pak hain
  80,15,likhnay walon ke hathon mein
  80,16,jo sardar aur naiko car hain
  80,17,ensaan halaak ho jaye kaisa nashukara hai
  80,18,ussay ( khuda ne ) kis cheez se banaya ?
  80,19,nutfay se banaya phir is ka andaza muqarrarkiya
  80,20,phir is ke liye rasta aasaan kar diya
  80,21,phir is ko mout di phir qabar mein dafan karaya
  80,22,phir jab chahay ga usay utha khara kere ga
  80,23,kuch shak nahi ke khuda ne usay jo hukum diya is ne is par amal nahkiya
  80,24,tu ensaan ko chahiye ke apne khanay ki taraf nazar kere
  80,25,be shak hum hi ne pani barsaya
  80,26,phir hum hi ne zameen ko cheera pharha
  80,27,phir hum hi ne is mein anaaj ugaya
  80,28,aur angoor aur tarkari
  80,29,aur Zaitoon aur khjorin
  80,30,aur ghany ghany baagh
  80,31,aur meway aur chara
  80,32,( yeh sab kuch ) tumahray aur tumahray charpayon ke liye banaya
  80,33,to jab ( qayamat ka ) ghul mache ga
  80,34,is din aadmi apne bhai se daur bhage ga
  80,35,aur apni maa aur apne baap se
  80,36,aur apni biwi aur apne betay se
  80,37,har shakhs is roz aik fikar mein ho ga jo usay ( masrufiyat ke liye ) bas kere ga
  80,38,aur kitney munh is roz chamak rahay hon ge
  80,39,Khandan o Shadan ( yeh mominan naiko car hain )
  80,40,aur kitney munh hon ge jin par gird par rahi ho gi
  80,41,( aur ) siyahi charh rahi ho gi
  80,42,yeh kufar badkirdar hain
